title: Cosmic Queries: Primate Evolution
description:
Paleoanthropologist Dr. Ian Tattersall is back to help Neil deGrasse Tyson and Eugene Mirman answer fan questions about where primates came from, and where we’re going.
Read more and listen to the full show at: http://www.startalkradio.net/show/cosmic-queries-primate-evolution
author: feed@startalkradio.net (Neil deGrasse Tyson)
